						               													<description>When opening Rendezvous in literature, the beautiful and charming ancient Chinese literature world is unfolded for you. So many characters, so many schemes and plots are entwined in these long speaking stories, forming the glamorous treasures that enchanted generations after generations of people. Let's travel through these masterpieces with this simple but fascinating game, and sympathize with those famous characters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;In this game, Qin Shihuang, the first emperor in ancient Chinese who once burned the books and buried alive the Confucian scholars, is back to live again. This time he tears apart all the characters and separate couples and families in Chinese literature. Being a talented sorcerer, you will help these characters by identifying their names and locating them in the right stories.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;During the game, you&amp;rsquo;ll need to get full understanding of the characters on your cards and speculate other players&amp;rsquo; hand. Then you can guess what cards others have. Once you got the right answer, take that card from player who own the card. And if you collect a whole set of characters, play them to get the corresponding scores. The one with highest scores is the winner.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
